entry   start
include 'win32ax.inc'
include 'api\kernel32.inc'
 

 
;------------------------------------------------             Создание переменных:
section '.data' data readable writeable
 
 
           n     dd  99  ; Переменная n (4 байта)
 
    sz_Hello     db  'Hello world ! n = %d', 10, 10, 0
;------------------------------------------------                   Код программы:
section '.code' code readable executable
 
 

 start:    mov eax,  65536
           mov  ax,  4



 L_03 :    cinvoke  printf, <"eax = %3d ", 10, 0>, eax
 
 L_04 :    cinvoke  scanf, <"%d", 10, 0>, n
           invoke   ExitProcess, 0
 
 
 
;------------------------------------------------           Подключение библиотек:
section '.idata' import data readable
library kernel32, 'kernel32.dll',\
        msvcrt,   'msvcrt.dll'
 
import msvcrt,\
       printf, 'printf',\
       scanf,  'scanf'

                "headline": "Flood Warning issued April 19 at 10:13AM CDT until April 23 at 1:00PM CDT by NWS Memphis TN",
                "description": "...The Flood Warning continues for the following rivers in\nArkansas...Mississippi...Tennessee...Missouri...\n\nMississippi River at Helena\n\nMississippi River at Memphis\n\nMississippi River at Tunica Mhoon Landing\n\nMississippi River Above Tiptonville\n\nMississippi River at Caruthersville\n\nMississippi River at Osceola\n\nFor the Lower Mississippi River...including Tiptonville,\nCaruthersville, Osceola, Memphis, Tunica Mhoon Landing, Helena...\nMajor flooding is forecast.\n\n* WHAT...Minor flooding is occurring and minor flooding is forecast.\n\n* WHERE...Mississippi River above Tiptonville.\n\n* WHEN...Until early Wednesday afternoon.\n\n* IMPACTS...At 40.0 feet, In Tennessee, long sections of Tiptonville\nFerry Road are flooded.\n\n* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...\n- At 10:00 AM CDT Saturday the stage was 41.3 feet.\n- Recent Activity...The maximum river stage in the 24 hours\nending at 9:00 AM CDT Saturday was 41.6 feet.\n- Forecast...The river is cresting and will fall below flood\nstage Wednesday morning.\n- Flood stage is 37.0 feet.\n- http://www.weather.gov/safety/flood",
                "instruction": "Motorists should not attempt to drive around barricades or drive\ncars through flooded areas.\n\nCaution is urged when walking near riverbanks.\n\nAdditional information is available at weather.gov/memphis.\n\nThe next statement will be issued as needed.",

## Ubuntu 25.04
 
## Opcional:
## Aperte CTRL + ALT + T e use este comando para ativar minimizar ao clicar:
~$ gsettings set org.gnome.shell.extensions.dash-to-dock click-action 'minimize'

~$ sudo -i
~# apt install aptitude -y ; aptitude install faac faad ffmpeg flac icedax id3v2 libjpeg-progs mjpegtools mpeg2dec mpeg3-utils mpegdemux mpg123 mpg321 regionset sox uudeview vorbis-tools x264 arj p7zip p7zip-full p7zip-rar rar unace-nonfree ubuntu-restricted-extras ubuntu-restricted-addons smplayer lame preload prelink dialog wine gimp gimp-gmic xsane devede k3b libk3b-dev libk3b-extracodecs libk3b8 ripperx audacity winff ssh nfs-common hardinfo samba htop frozen-bubble vim language-pack-kde-pt language-pack-pt-base language-pack-pt language-pack-gnome-pt-base language-pack-gnome-pt gnome-tweaks gnome-shell-extension-appindicator gnome-shell-extension-desktop-icons-ng gnome-shell-extension-gpaste gnome-shell-extensions gnome-software gnome-software-plugin-flatpak gnome-software-plugin-snap libdvdread8 libavcodec-extra libdvd-pkg libdvdread-dev libdvdread8t64 libreoffice libreoffice-gnome libreoffice-l10n-pt-br libreoffice-help-pt-br libreoffice-style-sifr zram-config mesa-utils libxss1 ifuse ppa-purge plocate locate proftpd exfat-fuse exfatprogs dosfstools inxi flatpak curl dkms stacer build-essential nala android-file-transfer net-tools psensor psensor-server guake menulibre libfuse2t64 gnome-epub-thumbnailer -y && snap install telegram-desktop vlc supertuxkart supertux && dpkg-reconfigure libdvd-pkg && cd /tmp && wget -c https://dl.google.com/linux/direct/google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb ; apt install ./google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb -y && nala upgrade -y && nala autoremove -y ; apt autoclean ; prelink -amRv ; updatedb ; exit

The course takes about 21 hours to finish . In the course, you will learn about algorithms, which are like secret recipes for computers . Knowing algorithms can help you get a job or create cool projects .
What you will learn
Make significant progress in programming (even if you are a complete beginner)
Master algorithms, from the simplest to the most complex (without being good at math or logic)
